# Daiquiri

> Simple and sublime, a delicate blend of rumâ€™s sweetness with the raw freshness of sugar and lime juice. #cocktail #rum

- Rum | White, 2 oz | 
- Simple Syrup | 1/2 oz | 
- Lime | 3/4 oz | Juiced

Combine ingredients in a boston shaker. Shake vigorously until the metal portion of the shaker is very cold and water has condensed on its surface.

- Lime | 1 wheel | 

Double strain into your glass and float a lime wheel on the surface.
